  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なによ、あのエルレインって人。
働かない事が幸せなんて、絶対間違ってる</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What's with that Elraine person?
Not having work being happiness is just plain wrong.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ていうか、わざわざそんな事言いに
出てきたのか？
あの聖女さん</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>More like, did she really come out just to say that?
That holy woman...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>いこう、リッド！
頑張る事の素晴らしさを
エルレインにも教えてあげなくちゃ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Let's go, Reid!
We've gotta teach Elraine how wonderful it is to have work!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
